    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this total gem. Honestly, it\u2019s a dream car\u2014it\u2019s been incredibly well-loved and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Everything is spotless, from the paint to the interior. I'm still building up my seller profile here, so I've priced it to move quickly. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see for yourself how perfect it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
