    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a definitive pinnacle of the S54-powered era. This specimen features a meticulously maintained 3.2L high-revving inline-six, with a high-pressure VANOS system that has been comprehensively serviced to ensure optimal cam phasing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to prevent the common floor-pan fatigue associated with this chassis. The exterior displays factory-perfect paint depth with no discernible imperfections, while the undercarriage retains its original cosmoline protection. Performance is sharpened by a fresh set of bushings and a recalibrated limited-slip differential, ensuring the mechanical grip and turn-in precision are as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. This is a turn-key collector piece for the uncompromising driver.",
